title: National FPO Samagam 2025: Over 500 Farmers from 24 States, 140 Districts to Showcase Agri Diversity in New Delhi
description: National FPO Samagam 2025 in New Delhi will bring together farmers, FPOs, and agri-experts to celebrate collective farming and rural innovation. The two-day event aims to strengthen farmer producer organizations through technology, value addition, and market linkages.
